bool VDRIVE::rsDiskCompare ( VDRIVE::RSDisk *  ld,
VDRIVE::RSDisk *  rd 
)

compare two RSDisks, needed to sort them. Returns if ld > rd. For two disks of same capacity it returns if ld.id < rd.id.

Parameters:
ldThe first disk
rdthe second disk
Returns:
ld > rd, for rd=ld ld.id < rd.id
